gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 120, Lakers 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Lakers, 120-101 tonight in Orlando. Franz Wagner contributed a team-high 26 points to go with 5 rebounds and two assists, with Paolo Banchero adding an additional 25 points (9-15 FG, 2-4 3P), 10 assists, and seven rebounds in the game. Anthony Davis finished with a team-high 28 points along with 13 rebounds and seven blocks for the Lakers in the losing effort. The Magic improve their record to 4-2 with the win, while the Lakers fall to 3-3 for the season.
